sources of PM&hyph;10 refer to activities where the human role in the cause of such emissions is highly attenuated
[see H.R. Rep. No. 490, 101st Cong., 2d Sess. 265 (1990)). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</FOOTNOTE>

