</FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
Implementation of RACM (including RACT) is required in all moderate PM&hyph;10 nonattainment areas and that requirement
is not waived under the provisions of section 188(f). Therefore, the issue is whether anthropogenic sources still
