 and other relevant materials for all source categories impacting the nonattainment area except those with a de minimis
impact considering emission reductions achieved with RACM.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

